text: Tage Wissnell (27 July 1905 - 13 May 1984) was a Swedish swimmer and footballer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Swedish footballers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm Category:Djurgårdens IF Fotboll players Category:Association footballers not categorized by position Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
